        "checksum": "6c458431854fd4228799e11720e8b88b7aa3d5814295a388fdaf24155e4d36c0_1_1_0_0__1",
        "ggSrZ5AP9Vh_text": "You Weren't Told the Full Story About Braces. Here's Another Perspective",
        "gglq6oGPrq9_text": "<p>Millions of people got braces to fix their smile. What they didn't know is it came at a cost —</p><p>and that cost is being paid every single day.</p>"
