        "ggx89wnuO3M_text": "<p>You spent years thinking your declining health was random. Or genetic. Or just bad luck.</p><p><br>&nbsp;<br>Now you know the truth. Your orthodontist didn't intend to damage you. But damage happened. And you've been living with the consequences.</p><p><br>&nbsp;<br>Reviv gives you a way to undo it.</p><p><br>&nbsp;<br>Not to manage it. Not to cover it up with supplements or therapy.<br>But to actually reverse the structural collapse and rebuild your foundation</p><p><br><br>The people in our community didn't wait. They started their recovery.&nbsp;</p><p>And they're experiencing transformations they thought were</p><p>impossible.</p><p><br><br>You can too.</p>"
